fields.name: sibling
fields.description: Choropleths are calculated using the sum of values of sibling geographies as the denominator. This is useful when comparing one geography with its siblings.

fields.name: subindicator
fields.description: Calculated using the sum of values of subindicators as the denominator. This is useful for presenting a per capita value.

fields.name: absolute_value
fields.description: This method displays the exact value as provided in the data.
